Package: bcgwcat
Type: Package
Title: BC Groundwater Chemistry Analysis Tool
Version: 0.5.1
Authors@R: c(person("Steffi", "LaZerte", email = "steffi@steffi.ca",
  role = c("aut", "cre")), 
  person("Andarge", "Baye", email = "Andarge.Baye@gov.bc.ca", role = "aut"),
  person("Province of British Columbia", role = "cph"))
Description: Set of tools for working with groundwater chemstry data from the 
    BC Government Environmental Monitoring System (EMS). Download EMS data via 
    the rems package and a) export for use in AquaChem, b) view water
    quality summaries, c) create piper and stiff plots. 
